text: No rabbits died during the entire experiment period. Of the 25 rabbits, 15 were found ON + (60%) and 10 were ON -(40%). Of the 15 ON + rabbits, 6 rabbits had only one ON lesion and were classified to SON group, 9 rabbits had more than one lesion and were classified into MON group. Histologically, ON lesion showed accumulation of marrow fat cells debris and bone trabeculae with many empty lacunae (Figure 1 ).
